dialog.getButton(androidx.appcompat.app.AlertDialog.BUTTON_POSITIVE)
 .setTextColor(getResources().getColor(R.color.green, requireContext().getTheme()));
dialog.getButton(androidx.appcompat.app.AlertDialog.BUTTON_NEGATIVE)
 .setTextColor(getResources().getColor(R.color.red, requireContext().getTheme()));
```

